EasyVFR cloud
Automatically :
EasyVFR stores routes, filed flightplans and aircraft profiles to servers located in the Netherlands owned by PocketFMS whenever there is an internet connection available and the associated item is saved.
Manually:
Logbook (includes tracking details), user waypoints, breadcrumb details are only stored on EasyVFR cloud when explicitly executed by the user.
